FBIS4-60180 "drnes099_j_94007" FBIS-NES-94-099 Daily Report 21 May 1994 ARABIAN PENINSULA Yemen Southern Yemen To Announce Secession From North Southern Yemen To Announce Secession From North Al-Iryani Denies Russian Action NC2105152094 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1505 GMT 21 May 94 NC2105152094 Cairo MENA Arabic BFN [Text] Sanaa, 21 May (MENA)--Dr. 'Abd-al-Karim al-Iryani, Yemeni minister of planning and development, has denied that Russia has recognized the Yemeni Democratic Republic, saying that apparently there has been a misunderstanding.
